						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Climate-change/Related-developments/Coffee-leaf-rust-is-spreading-through-the-Americas" title="Coffee leaf rust is spreading through the Americas" alt="link">Coffee leaf rust is spreading through the Americas</a></h2>

	
					<p>This research demonstrates the importance of nutritional factors, fruit loads, fertilization and soil quality in mitigating the impacts and spread of the fungus, and how climate change influences epidemics.<a href="http://www.cirad.fr/en/news/all-news-items/press-releases/2013/leaf-rust" target="_self">http://www.cirad.fr/en/news/all-news-items/press-releases/2013/leaf-rust</a>(CIRAD, 15/03/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Climate-change/Related-developments/Coffee-leaf-rust-is-spreading-through-the-Americas">Read more...</a>
